CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Pyramids - New members of the Delta Sigma Theta Sorority's pledge club, the Pyramid, at the U. of Pittsburgh, are Dorothy Pridgen and Carrie Warley. They were feted at the home of Soror Susie Boone. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Delta Sigma Theta Sorority pledges Dorothy Pridgen wearing light colored sleeveless dress with dot pattern on scoop neck collar, and Carrie Warley, holding gift in hands, standing in home of Susie Boone with zigzag patterned sofa, decorative lamps, and geometrically patterned curtains
